==Finnish==
===Adjective===
''vittuuntunut'' 

# Angry as a cunt; describing a person experiencing [[vitutus]]. Some females may like to use the word ''[[kyrpiintynyt]]'' instead, which is derived from the word for [[prick]].

Derived from [[vittu]].

===Adjective: Comparative levels===

''vittuuntuneempi'' "more deeply annoyed [than someone, or at a specified time]". Seldom used

''vittuuntunein'' "most deeply annoyed [in the group in question]". Very seldom used, almost extinct.

